title: The Journal of Sir Walter Scott; From the Original Manuscript at Abbotsford
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: _August_ 21.--Wrote four pages, then set out to make a call atSunderland Hall and Yair, but the old sociable broke down before we hadgot past the thicket, so we trudged all back on foot, and I wroteanother page.
